			<p>During all this construction I began working on my own tomb and burial chamber. It's eerie to work on something that I know I will never use, because I plan to live forever. Nevertheless, it's comforting to know I have a nice resting place should the unthinkable happen. It is place on the same level as the river, so I can hear the monstrous carp float by.</p>
			<p><a href="images/suc_img/autumnpicJPG_5e28eqv66j.jpg"><img class="left" src="images/suc_img/autumnpicJPG_5e28eqv66j.jpg" /></a>Well Autumn is finally here and my project this season was to build a stone wall around the steps up top, that way I can funnel any bad guys into the stone fall traps I'm going to put there!</p><div class="clear"></div>
			<p>These traps are paying off already, a Giant Slug happened to get in one of the stone fall traps and squish goes the slug!</p>
