            <p><a href="images/suc_img/migrants2JPG_kqzepypacp.jpg"><img class="right" src="images/suc_img/migrants2JPG_kqzepypacp.jpg" /></a>More Migrants arrived this fall, which brings out total up to 18 dwarfs in CrestedGilt! You can also see the beginnings of the Main Hall in this picture as well. We need a place to sit and drink our brew and eat our food in peace, and I think this is one of the places to do it in! When new migrants come, they will come here and admire how awesome it is. (Note this is only a temporary hall mind you, my job is to get this place ship shape before the new spring, this can be moved deeper down in the stone at a later time.)</p>
